#### API Summary

##### Read Items
* [GetUserItem](#capi-useritems-getuseritem) - Retrieves the identified user item from the server.
* [GetUserItemsPage](#capi-useritems-getuseritemspage) - Retrieves the page of user's items from the server based on the context. 
* [GetUserItemsPageOffset](#capi-useritems-getuseritemspageoffset) - Retrieves the page of user's items from the server based on the encoded context. 

##### Affect Item Owner
* [AwardUserItem](#capi-useritems-awarduseritem) - Allows item(s) to be awarded to a user without collecting the purchase amount. 
* [DropUserItem](#capi-useritems-dropuseritem) - Allows a quantity of a specified user item to be dropped, without any recovery of the money paid for the item. 
* [SellUserItem](#capi-useritems-selluseritem) - Allows a quantity of a specified user item to be sold. 
* [GiveUserItemTo](#capi-useritems-giveuseritemto) - Gifts item to the specified player.
* [ReceiveUserItemFrom](#capi-useritems-receiveuseritemfrom) - Retrieves and transfers the gift item from the specified player, who must have previously called giveUserItemTo.
* [PurchaseUserItem](#capi-useritems-purchaseuseritem) - Purchases a quantity of an item from the specified store, if the user has enough funds. 

##### Edit Item State
* [UseUserItem](#capi-useritems-useuseritem) - Uses the specified item, potentially consuming it.
* [UpdateUserItemData](#capi-useritems-updateuseritemdata) - Updates the item data on the specified user item.

##### Blockchain 
* [PublishUserItemToBlockchain](#capi-useritems-publishuseritemtoblockchain) - Publishes the specified item to the item management attached blockchain. 
* [RefreshBlockchainUserItems](#capi-useritems-refreshblockchainuseritems) - Syncs the caller's user items with the item management attached blockchain. 